data.description: Charming Home Near Fort Stewart - $208,000 Welcome to 996 Pineland Avenue, a cozy and convenient home located in Hinesville, GA 31313. This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence spans 1120 sq ft and boasts a range of appealing features. The property offers a spacious kitchen with a dining area, perfect for gatherings and meal prep. The bedrooms are inviting, with carpeting in two of them for added comfort. A storage room provides additional space for your belongings. Outside, you'll find a fenced backyard and a shed, ideal for outdoor activities and storage needs. The property's location is convenient, close to Fort Stewart and all shopping amenities. This home has no HOA fees, and the seller is offering a $5,000 contribution towards closing costs. Don't miss this opportunity to own a lovely home in a great location!
